728293f-c.title: Richmond: Altamount Street - Beacon Avenue
728293f-c.text:
(1)
Altamount Street, west side, between Beacon Avenue and
Kildare Street, showing the Eew Dorp Lighthouse. The beacon
is about 150 feet back of the street.
1924
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2) The same, another view.

An additional view.
